net.objectzoo.ebc.join

Class ObjectAndCollectionOutputCreator<Input1,Input2Element,OutputElement>

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.objectzoo.ebc.join.ObjectAndCollectionOutputCreator<Input1,Input2Element,OutputElement>
  • Type Parameters:
    Input1 - the type of the first input of this Join output creator
    Input2Element - the element type of the second input collection two of this Join output creator
    OutputElement - the element type of the output list of this Join output creator
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    JoinOutputCreator<Input1,java.util.Collection<Input2Element>,java.util.List<OutputElement>>

    public class ObjectAndCollectionOutputCreator<Input1,Input2Element,OutputElement>
extends java.lang.Object
implements JoinOutputCreator<Input1,java.util.Collection<Input2Element>,java.util.List<OutputElement>>
    This JoinOutputCreator implementation takes a first input and a Collection of input elements and creates a List of output elements that contains an output element for each element present in the second input constructed together with the given first input.
    Author:
    tilmann
